    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "RUQ pain\nHigh\nfever\nNausea\n,\nvomiting\n, anorexia\nClay-colored stool\nDark urine\nJaundice\n- seen with pyogenic, as opposed to amebic\n[1]\nOften with right\npleural effusions",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": []
    },
