          "text": "Pyogenic abscess\nAerobic:\nEscherichia coli\n,\nKlebsiella\n,\nPseudomonas\nAnaerobic:\nEnterococcus\n,\nbacteroides\n, anaerobic\nstreptococci\nEchinococcosis\nAmebiasis\nBenign cysts/malignancy\nTuberculosis\nMycosis",
          "tables": []
